cs.CV, cs.RO, cs.LG, cs.GR, cs.CG 

The paper deals with the problem of camera geometry computation in structure from motion, which is a common topic in computer vision (cs.CV) and robotics (cs.RO). The use of homotopy continuation techniques and optimization methods also suggests a connection to machine learning (cs.LG). The paper also involves geometric reasoning and analysis, which falls under computational geometry (cs.CG) and graphics (cs.GR).
